STATUS: Draft
SOURCE: Speculation
PRIORITY: Must
TITLE: Visible indication of digital hardware held in reset
STATEMENT: >>>
Engineering Students need consumer hardware to give a visible indication that the digital electronics is held in reset.
<<<
RATIONALE: >>>
Digital hardware that is held in reset is necessarily powered, indicating a need for heightened safety awareness. Digital electronics that is held in reset indicates the digital electronics is **not** executing a computer program.
<<<
