TITLE: Youth

[NEED]
MID: 1ae60ab0930d4a1f94cb996022eb4e67
UID: STKNEED-3
STATUS: Draft
SOURCE: Observation
PRIORITY: Must
TITLE: Visible device alive indication soon after applying power
STATEMENT: >>>
Youth need a visible indication that a consumer electronics device is alive soon after applying power to the consumer electronics device.
<<<
RATIONALE: >>>
Youth experiment with connections and have very little patience for devices that do not immediately seem to "work". The visible indication appearing soon after applying power gives the youth quick feedback on whether the device is actually powered and expected to be functional
<<<
