[NEED]
MID: 449be10602d24613b44babd186cdd39a
UID: STKNEED-5
STATUS: Draft
SOURCE: Speculation
PRIORITY: Must
TITLE: Visible indication of "bricked" device
STATEMENT: >>>
Youth need a visible indication on a device for when the device is no longer usable and not able to receive a FW update.
<<<
RATIONALE: >>>
Devices may become unusable due to corrupted persistent data, expired certificates, or being explicitly revoked by a device owner. The critical need is to indicate between a device that knows it is no longer usable vs a device that may be recovered through a reset and/or a FW update.
<<<
